<p begin="31870597508t" end="31878937506t" region="region.after" style="defaultStyle" xml:id="subtitle838">[gasps]</p>
<p begin="31916055003t" end="31949842507t" region="region.after" style="defaultStyle" xml:id="subtitle839">[Steve] <span style="defaultStyle_2">They say when a nuclear holocaust</span><br/><span style="defaultStyle_2">destroys the world,</span></p>
