<p begin="32540850007t" end="32552519999t" region="region.after" style="defaultStyle" xml:id="subtitle858">OK.</p>
<p begin="32553355000t" end="32583385000t" region="region.after" style="defaultStyle" xml:id="subtitle859"><span style="defaultStyle_2">We had no idea</span><br/><span style="defaultStyle_2">what we were in for.</span></p>
